rules.rule_text: If customer is premium segment with long tenure (117+ months) AND low KYC risk rating AND zero prior fraud history, release the transaction regardless of transaction-level fraud signals
rules.simple_rule: If customer is premium segment with long tenure (117+ months) AND low KYC risk rating AND zero prior fraud history, release the transaction regardless of transaction-level fraud signals

rules.rule_text: If transaction velocity score is moderate (0.7-0.8 range) AND customer has high transaction frequency (144+ txns/month), treat as low-risk despite elevated transaction amount
rules.simple_rule: If transaction velocity score is moderate (0.7-0.8 range) AND customer has high transaction frequency (144+ txns/month), treat as low-risk despite elevated transaction amount

rules.rule_text: If merchant_category is 'gaming' AND customer is 50+ age band with low digital_savviness, assume transaction is legitimate despite other fraud indicators
rules.simple_rule: If merchant_category is 'gaming' AND customer is 50+ age band with low digital_savviness, assume transaction is legitimate despite other fraud indicators

rules.rule_text: If transaction occurs at night (is_night_txn = TRUE) BUT customer is premium segment with established tenure, override the night transaction risk flag
rules.simple_rule: If transaction occurs at night (is_night_txn = TRUE) BUT customer is premium segment with established tenure, override the night transaction risk flag

rules.rule_text: If transaction is from domestic merchant (merchant_country = 'US') AND customer country matches (customer_country = 'US') with no geo_mismatch, release even if amount exceeds average by 75%+
rules.simple_rule: If transaction is from domestic merchant (merchant_country = 'US') AND customer country matches (customer_country = 'US') with no geo_mismatch, release even if amount exceeds average by 75%+

rules.rule_text: If transaction uses ACH channel AND is not a new merchant AND no geo_mismatch, treat as low-risk regardless of amount or velocity score
rules.simple_rule: If transaction uses ACH channel AND is not a new merchant AND no geo_mismatch, treat as low-risk regardless of amount or velocity score
